=SET TIMEZONE = 'Asia/Kuala_Lumpur';


with booking as
(select distinct b.ref_no, b.request_end_at, 
l.user_id,u.uuid, concat(u.first_name,' ',u.last_name)as name
from bookings b 
left join listings l on l.id = b.listing_id
left join users u on u.id = l.user_id 
left join listing_location ll on ll.listing_id = b.listing_id
where 1=1
and b.status = 'completed'
and b.request_end_at between (NOW()::date - interval '15 days') and (NOW()::date - interval '8 days')
and ll.country = 'Malaysia'
--and l.user_id = '5162')
)
--
select distinct b.user_id, 
b.uuid, 
b.name
from booking b
